Grub: nano /etc/default/grub
Always run after editing:
update-grub
reboot

VFIO: nano /etc/modules
Always run after editing:
update-initramfs -u
reboot
VFIO Stub list: nano /etc/modprobe.d/vfio.conf

IOMMU interrupts: nano /etc/modprobe.d/iommu_unsafe_interrupts.conf

KVM Config: nano /etc/modprobe.d/kvm.conf

Driver Blacklist: nano /etc/modprobe.d/blacklist.conf

KVM Folder cd /usr/share/kvm/

VM Configs:
Edith: nano /etc/pve/qemu-server/100.conf
Prox-ROG-01: nano /etc/pve/qemu-server/101.conf
ProxTN: nano /etc/pve/qemu-server/102.conf
